description: Removes tags from the specified container. You can specify one or more tags to remove.

parameters.name: Resource
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the container.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A comma-separated list of keys for tags that you want to remove from the container. For example, if your container has two tags (customer:CompanyA and priority:High) and you want to remove one of the tags (priority:High), you specify the key for the tag that you want to remove (priority). (string) ---
